title: Anyone know where i can find 'Get Jinxed' as a Bass tab?

embed.description: Jinx's dreams come alive in a hexplosive sequence packed with bombs and bullets and her unique take on fun. Marvel at the mayhem in the Jinx music video. Vocals by: Agnete Kj√∏lsrud from the band Djerv. Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/leagueoflegends/get-jinxed Lyrics: [Intro] Blah blah blablah. [Verse 1] Wanna join me, come and play.

body:
I want to learn Jinx's theme from the music video on bass guitar but i suck at music and cant work it out by ear.

so if anyone knows where i can find the Bass Guitar Tableture, please let me know.

also if anyone knows Tahm Kench as well that would be appreciated ^^

replies.body:
Get Jinxed tab is [here](http://www.songsterr.com/a/wsa/league-of-legends-get-jinxed-tab-s386009t6). Just select the instrument from the drop down menu at the top. 

As for the Tahm Kench theme, your best option is to go for guitar tab, and make some small adjustments from there for bass. You'll need to know a tiny bit of music theory, but it should be relatively easy. 

I actually did a Guitar Cover for the Tahm Kench with downloadable tabs in the description. Check it out [here](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pItH8vPFluY), if you're interested.

If you're struggling with anything, feel free to get in contact with me. I can give you a hand if you need.

Thanks so much man!
I'm afraid music isn't my strong suit but I do want to get back into playing the bass again and what better to play than league stuff xD
Thanks I will :)
